products.shortDescription: Enjoy simple solutions for copying, burning and saving your files
products.longDescription: Technology — it's constantly changing, especially when it comes to media and the way we're able to access and enjoy it. The world is inundated with mobile devices. From cell phones and tablets to e-readers and more, you need your media to be as flexible and portable as your devices are. Now, there's a simple solution for mobilizing your media library — 123 Copy DVD. This software makes it easy to copy, burn and save your files, so you can get the most out of your entertainment collection.  123 Copy DVD works with a variety of popular file formats, including MKV, H.264, MP4, AVI, DivX, XViD and WMV, making it easy to create DVDs from your favorite blockbuster hits, Internet videos or home movies. Back up your entire media collection by making a copy of all of your DVDs. Make a copy with Quick-Play and you can even remove distracting, time-consuming ads. Burn downloaded movies to play in standard DVD players or save them to compatible mobile devices, such as select Apple® iPhone®, iPad® and iPod® models, Android cell phones and tablets, PSPs, PlayStation 3 and Xbox 360 consoles, Kindle Fire and more. 123 Copy DVD gives you the flexibility to make exact 1:1 copies or compressed versions of your favorite movies. Managing your media in this constantly evolving digital age doesn't have to be hard — in fact, it can be as easy as 123.
